title: Dreams are now a reality! Res Lease in San Marcos. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ['Now this is the perfect opportunity for you to lease!!', 'Come and check out this lovely 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in San Marcos, TX.', 'You will love everything this home has to offer; from its wood floors, spacious living area, cozy fireplace and the well designed kitchen that comes with plenty of storage space, large pantry, elegant cabinetry and stainless steel appliances perfect for any home chef.', 'All the bedrooms feature ample space and ceiling fans to keep the house cool on the hotter Texas nights.', "Tour and apply today before it's gone!!", 'Application must be submitted to schedule showing', '**', 'All renters are enrolled in the resident benefits package.', 'Reach out for more details  *** Send Text Message FEDERICO to', '--to set up a viewing--', 'Call/Text/Email ANYTIME!', 'Federico Argueta', 'show contact info', '(ask for ID# 3556060)', 'All City Real Estate Company', 'Have other properties available....', '(Houses, Duplexes, Apartments, Condos, All Areas)', 'Please be Aware of SCAMS...', 'Do NOT reply to this ad, please call/text for a fast response.', 'Listed By: Benjamin Doherty, Sunroom Rentals Texas, LLC']
